arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start()

	--Donan Bark + Move Loc1 + Anim
	Hydra.Wait(1.5)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONVO_DONAN_01, ID_DONAN_TOWER)
	Hydra.QActorEventSend(ID_DONAN_TOWER, "VERGE4_DONAN_FAIL")

end

function Start()
	Hydra.ActorWarpToActor(ID_DONAN_TOWER, LOC_DONAN_01)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(ID_DONAN_TOWER, LOC_DONAN_01)
	Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(ID_DONAN_TOWER, ANIMSET_STAND_USE)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(ID_DONAN_TOWER)
end

function Start()

	--Donan Move and Use + Taissa Move 
	Hydra.Wait(1.5)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONVO_TAISSA_01, ID_TAISSA_TOWER)
	
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_TAISSA_TOWER, LOC_TAISSA_EXIT, "NPC_WALK_FAST", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(ID_TAISSA_TOWER, LOC_TAISSA_EXIT)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(ID_TAISSA_TOWER)
	Hydra.QActorEventSend(ID_TAISSA_TOWER, "VERGE5_TAISSA_OUTSIDE")
	
end

function Start()

	--Donan to Loc2 
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_DONAN_TOWER, LOC_DONAN_02, "NPC_WALK_FAST", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(ID_DONAN_TOWER, LOC_DONAN_02)
	Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(ID_DONAN_TOWER, ANIMSET_STAND_USE)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(ID_DONAN_TOWER)

	--Donan Fizzle + Explode + Bark + Anim 
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroupActorToActor(ID_DONAN_TOWER, ID_SOULSTONE_FX, FX_SOULSTONE_ROPE, true)
	Hydra.QActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_DONAN_TOWER, VFX_FIZZLE)
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONVO_DONAN_05, ID_DONAN_TOWER)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ID_DONAN_TOWER, CONVO_DONAN_05)
	Hydra.QActorPlayEffectGroup(ID_DONAN_TOWER, VFX_EXPLOSION)
	Hydra.QActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(ID_DONAN_TOWER, FX_SOULSTONE_ROPE)
	Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(ID_DONAN_TOWER, ANIMSET_DONAN_SMASH)
	Hydra.QActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONVO_DONAN_09, ID_DONAN_TOWER)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ID_DONAN_TOWER, CONVO_DONAN_09)
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ID_DONAN_TOWER, CONVO_DONAN_05)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(ID_DONAN_TOWER)

	Hydra.QActorEventSend(ID_DONAN_TOWER, "VERGE4_DONAN_PAIN")
	
end
